name: ChanceStarship

Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chance starship
des:
Chance Starship is a randomly generated space adventure. You need to find enough energy cells to fix space craft while trying not to run out of food or succumb to the dangers aboard.
Map out the starship and see where it takes you,

Also see the "Chance Dungeon" skill.

Interested in writing your own story ? 
See https://sharemetale.wordpress.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
